{"tid":373863,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"浪費左5年時間，今日先知自己唔適合這份工","createTime":"2017-08-25T10:31:45.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-25T16:29:15.000Z","uid":80154,"like":2,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"77ac004c301e1105f61d69379ba2c51aa5afc997","tid":373863,"uid":80154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T10:31:45.000Z","msg":"岩岩出來做野時，抱著得過且過心態。<br />\n果時的自己唔知想點，總之有野做就得。<br />\n甘就入左間大公司做，想著穩定點。<br />\n對自己的工作可以話沒熱誠，也看不到希望。<br />\n成日對自己講有糧出，有假放就得。<br />\n曾經想轉行，但又沒踏出著步得勇氣。<br />\n自己的適應能力很差，怕去到新環境適應唔到。<br />\n份工來講系穩定，簽長約後也不怕被炒。<br />\n但系自己有事唔知自己系度做緊乜。<br />\n今日先知自己浪費時間，我可以點？<br />\n轉行就等於重新來過，唔轉我又唔甘心。<br />\n我宜家好矛盾<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd7e9cd7be6f8288213742b1f48df5794f3dadef","tid":373863,"uid":72420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T10:34:54.000Z","msg":"睇下你將來想為做過而後悔定無做過而後悔"},{"pid":"7d6b50fc2f5743e100495953409b4e92f8654183","tid":373863,"uid":135019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T10:36:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />做左5年design, 發現根本揾笨然後轉行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2b319d1229bf35ab1c844e5fa78b53c09ba7d2f","tid":373863,"uid":48006,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T10:58:02.000Z","msg":"我係咪自己開緊post?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"babb01c639dcb1317316cb930a850d996f0fb6bf","tid":373863,"uid":18241,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T10:59:46.000Z","msg":"甘你老母<br />\n<br />\n系你老母"},{"pid":"4108f5ca492e60868263c1c78a26b8b181397fa7","tid":373863,"uid":37733,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T11:01:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>甘你老母<br />\n<br />\n系你老母